org.apache.poi.hssf.dev

Class FormulaViewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.dev.FormulaViewer

  • public class FormulaViewer
extends java.lang.Object
    FormulaViewer - finds formulas in a BIFF8 file and attempts to read them/display data from them. Only works if Formulas are enabled in "RecordFactory"(FormulaViewer -在BIFF 8文件中查找公式并尝试读取它们/显示其中的数据。仅在“RecordFactory”中启用公式时有效)
    Author:
    andy, Avik
